üöÄ 4. Performance & Security

‚úÖ Helmet & Compression

`js
const helmet = require('helmet');
const compression = require('compression');
app.use(helmet());
app.use(compression());
`

‚úÖ Output:
- Security headers added.
- Faster response times.

